{"tid":8873,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"LIHKG香港女神聯賽正式啟動!歡迎各位巴打踴躍提名","createTime":"2016-11-28T12:57:27.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-05T13:08:05.000Z","uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"93544b76c6696f508a60db6cff099f5171e38f27","tid":8873,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:57:27.000Z","msg":"因為娛樂台出唔到吹水台,新黎唔知唯有開多次,呢個至作準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎各位巴打踴躍提名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG香港女神聯賽選拔須知:\t\t\t\t\t<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t<br />\n提名期由現在至12月8日0:00止\t\t\t\t\t<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t<br />\n每位會員可任意提名不同的女藝人/名人參與聯賽\t\t\t\t\t<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t<br />\n會員可提名超過一次，惟新增侯補提名不能重覆\t\t\t\t\t<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t<br />\n會員必須在回覆內打出:本人提名(姓名)[{如有更多提名者請按右列格式繼續提名}:、(姓名)、(姓名)．．．]參加2016-17LIHKG香港女神聯賽(任何組別)，否則提名將不計算在內\t\t\t\t\t<br />\n聯賽資格說明:\t\t\t\t\t<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t<br />\n最高提名票之16位女藝員/名人可以獲參加頂級聯賽(超聯)的資格<br />\n若有最後一位的提名票相同，將以資格附加賽決定最後一席誰屬<br />\n<br />\n而票數不及首16位者，則參與次一級冠聯比賽，惟此列最少有18人，否則將不開設冠聯\t\t\t\t<br />\n如有更大量的參賽女神而又有足夠人手，或會進一步開設甲組及乙組聯賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家提名心水女神,爭奪殊榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aedd5d10db38a808a07caafea6985ca3e6dba26","tid":8873,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:59:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1b8e328dd4698dcfa6356de1ea36ace34e7e80","tid":8873,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T13:04:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"deb5634ccd7c91a4699727233984558e68b0db1d","tid":8873,"uid":26931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T13:05:18.000Z","msg":"魯芬bb"},{"pid":"83b1cf0154ae0ae98b909a7fb31f616a90f8eac5","tid":8873,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T13:05:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>魯芬bb</blockquote><br />\n跟返格式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d05ad88d3840bf26248ecc096aa6238d4ace83c3","tid":8873,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T13:09:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48ca354df1e64cf43d5f83d1374071b5941faf5c","tid":8873,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:17:48.000Z","msg":"本人提名林ee林依麗參加2016-17LIHKG香港女神聯賽(任何組別)<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n\t\t\t\t\t<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i4/sUiSW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi4%2FsUiSW.jpg&h=97609868&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae15a8c6754e45518526ac3b1cd02ccd44cab15d","tid":8873,"uid":31472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:07:37.000Z","msg":"本人提名 謝安琪 參加2016-17LIHKG香港女神聯賽"},{"pid":"4922d8842c0e663925abac615adf5c2c7d0c3ff9","tid":8873,"uid":1637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:01:14.000Z","msg":"本人提名 黎姿 參加2016-17LIHKG香港女神聯賽(任何組別)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2vGyO5B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2vGyO5B.jpg&h=a42cb9b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c41ac7a1ffdfc039ef912d4ef86dff9ae2b65192","tid":8873,"uid":42574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:37:30.000Z","msg":"本人提名趙慧珊，陳穎欣，李靜儀，黃子菲參加2016-17LIHKG香港女神聯賽(任何組別)"},{"pid":"5a74dd9889f3ad2ad2f1da75b49231409e260756","tid":8873,"uid":50727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T13:08:05.000Z","msg":"本人提名趙慧珊，蘇麗珊，袁澧林參加2016-17LIHKG香港女神聯賽(任何組別)"}]}